  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "二项式定理及其衍生",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>交错和为 0</strong>：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$ \\sum_{i=0}^n (-1)^i \\binom{n}{i} = 0 \\quad (n > 0) $$",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>偶数项之和 = 奇数项之和</strong>：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$ \\sum_{i \\text{ 为偶数}} \\binom{n}{i} = \\sum_{i \\text{ 为奇数}} \\binom{n}{i} = 2^{n-1} $$",
          "depth": 3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "经典求和公式",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>上指标求和</strong>：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$ \\sum_{i=k}^n \\binom{i}{k} = \\binom{n+1}{k+1} $$",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<em>(应用场景：求</em> $1 \\sim n$ <em>的组合数之和，常用于转化前缀和问题)</em>",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "例题： <a href=\"/p/abc154f-many-many-paths\" class=\"wikilink\">ABC154F Many Many Paths</a>",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>平行求和（下指标变化，上指标跟着变）</strong>：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$ \\sum_{i=0}^k \\binom{n+i}{i} = \\binom{n+k+1}{k} $$",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>部分交错和（截断求和）</strong>：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "通常交错和必须加到 $n$ 才是 0，如果只加到 $m$ 呢？",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$ \\sum_{i=0}^m (-1)^i \\binom{n}{i} = (-1)^m \\binom{n-1}{m} $$",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<em>(这个公式在容斥原理优化时间复杂度时极其关键！)</em>",
          "depth": 3
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
